text: Máximo González and André Sá were the defending champions, but chose to compete in Kitzbühel and Gstaad, respectively, instead. Martin Kližan and David Marrero won the title, defeating Nikola Mektić and Antonio Šančić in the final, 6–4, 6–2. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== * Main Draw Croatia Open Umag - Singles 2016 Singles Category:2016 in Croatian sport
